{"tid":1069783,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"我啱啱俾個人掉左落垃圾桶","createTime":"2019-03-20T07:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T08:33:52.000Z","uid":209308,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"829dd1212a6b7ed14ce99db5a1c3e1092c38fc98","tid":1069783,"uid":209308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:50:17.000Z","msg":"是咁的，話說公司放lunch 咁主人搞埋少少手尾就入pantry諗住叮我嚟食啦<br />\n<br />\n點知一入去就見到個微波爐有盒唔知乜撚野雞扒茄子飯喺裡面<br />\n主人心諗邊條仆街叮完又唔拎返出黎 人又唔知去左邊<br />\n<br />\n咁主人就幫個同事拎返佢盒飯擺喺個爐上面 再放我落去叮啦<br />\n<br />\n咁我本來仲暖暖地嘅 咁主人咪諗住撳兩分鐘熱一熱吓我就算<br />\n之後叮左差唔多四十零五十秒主諗應該夠熱啦就停左個爐拎返我走<br />\n點知呢個時候有個唔係好熟嘅嘅黐線佬同事入左黎<br />\n<br />\n一入黎見波爐上面個計時寫住1分幾鐘就當堂發晒矛咁問主人做乜撚嘢事，又話咩主人無禮貌<br />\n<br />\n主人都唔知佢做乜撚野<br />\n雖然主都知佢係痴痴地嗰啲人黎，但係都廢事惹佢啦<br />\n係咁咦講兩句唔好意思就閃人算<br />\n<br />\n跟住佢一手搶左我 之後倒落個垃圾桶度<br />\n<br />\nWhat The Fuck !?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n主人心諗屌你老母真係唔知佢發乜撚野癲<br />\n<br />\n我都心諗屌你老母真係唔知佢發乜撚野癲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後主人嬲撚到將成件事上報比老細聽 佢聽到都好撚嬲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啱啱仲收到風話咩個老細叫位同事返屋企休息兩日添<br />\n<br />\n唔知佢嚟緊呢兩日係屋企會唔會搵定下份工先呢<br />\n<br />\n好撚無辜啊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37a1f622acec5bc596d9813e068e990feef7930","tid":1069783,"uid":62822,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:50:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc3e12cb2b9f4ece6f108a4d02293a011fb15865","tid":1069783,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:55:01.000Z","msg":"垃圾桶角度有未"},{"pid":"034158993f856ed9d0534e3be82eeb8edc0666d8","tid":1069783,"uid":121259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:57:41.000Z","msg":"老細聽完雙方證供, 可唔可以上嚟比返個完整故事我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b2065f3a455b1464d21ac2d65983170003c304","tid":1069783,"uid":113912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:58:39.000Z","msg":"老細角度呢?<br />\n仲有仲有 你地知唔知微波爐都有生命嫁"},{"pid":"f184392c7376bb68183bfdb013c530997b852266","tid":1069783,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T08:11:41.000Z","msg":"你而家喺老細房垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你點知老細覆乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4358b0e7969d93f845ab56f55353fdf3004609c9","tid":1069783,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T08:24:40.000Z","msg":"潮文咩係咁改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d33e4ba57c8b8db70c40c8b8ddeb53947b25be9","tid":1069783,"uid":209308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f184392c7376bb68183bfdb013c530997b852266","tid":1069783,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T08:11:41.000Z","msg":"你而家喺老細房垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你點知老細覆乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T08:33:52.000Z","msg":"重睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}